getDimensionFilters

public List<DimensionValue> getDimensionFilters()
The list of filters on which dimensions are filtered. Filters for different dimensions are ANDed, filters for the same dimension are grouped together and ORed. A valid active GRP report needs to have exactly one DimensionValue for the United States in addition to any advertiser or campaign dimension values. The value returned may be null.
